{
  "text": "<Parameters for tripole model> As to the tripole model, following parameters were used\uff1b conductivity of the volume conductor was [CITATION_1] . The distance between I 1 and I 2 was 0.45 mm, and that between I 2 and I 3 was 1.8 mm [CITATION_2] . The conduction velocity v was 3.5 (m/s) [CITATION_3] .",
